description:
Demolition of existing part two storey building (Use Class E) and construction of a part three storey residential building (Use Class
C3) to provide 6 self contained 1 bedroom flats and a three storey, 3 bedroom dwelling house with associated cycle parking, refuse storage and private amenity space in the form
of balconies and terraces, a green roof and a green living wall.&nbsp;
